"33:72:11" : {s: 33, a: 72, w: 11, r: "شفق", t: "وَأَشْفَقْنَ", l: "أَشْفَقْ", lc: 2, tl: "wa-ashfaqna", lb: "ভীত হওয়া, ভয় পাওয়া",e: "and they feared", b: "আর তারা ভয় পেল", i: "dan mereka merasa takut", f: 1, rm: "to pity, be anxious about, fear. shafaq - fear, pity, evening, twilight with its redness or whiteness, after sunset. ashfaqa - to be afraid. mushfiqun - one who is afraid or is in terror, compassionate, fearful one, tender.", ag: "واو عطف وفعل ماض صيغة ٤ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Conjunction wa and Verb Perfect 4th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "(IV)", deg: "3", gen: "F", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "مُشْفِقُونَ"},
