"33:72:17" : {s: 33, a: 72, w: 17, r: "ظلم", t: "ظَلُومًۭا", l: "ظَلُوم", lc: 2, tl: "ẓalūman", lb: "অত্যাচারী",e: "unjust", b: "বড় জালিম", i: "amat zalim", f: 1, rm: "", ag: "أسم نكرة", eg: "Noun Indefinite state", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "INDEF", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "أَظْلَمَ،أَظْلَمُ،ظَلَمَ"},
"33:72:18" : {s: 33, a: 72, w: 18, r: "جهل", t: "جَهُولًۭا", l: "جَهُول", lc: 1, tl: "jahūlan", lb: "অজ্ঞ, মুর্খ",e: "ignorant", b: "বড় অজ্ঞ", i: "amat bodoh", f: 1, rm: "To be ignorant, not know of a thing, to be silly or foolish, boil vehemently, pretend ignorance, feign ignorance, reckon or esteem someone, cause commotion or unsteadiness, display wrong conduct, to be void of knowledge, believe a thing to be different from what it is in reality, do a thing in a manner different from that in which it ought to be done, proceed without knowledge, to ignore a thing, to be pagan.", ag: "صفة نكرة", eg: "Adjective Indefinite state", tag: "ADJ", pos: "ADJ", att: "INDEF", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "جَٰهِلُونَ"},
"33:73:1" : {s: 33, a: 73, w: 1, r: "عذب", t: "لِّيُعَذِّبَ", l: "عَذَّبَ", lc: 41, tl: "liyuʿadhiba", lb: "শাস্তি দেওয়া, আযাব দেওয়া",e: "So that Allah may punish", b: "(এর পরিণাম হল এই যে) শাস্তি দিবেন", i: "karena akan menyiksa", f: 1, rm: "chastisement, castigate, punishment, torture, torment, retribution, abstain/desist (e.g. from eating due to excessive thirst), relinquish, quit. To deny a thing, hinder anyone from, be inaccessible, prevent.", ag: "لام التعليل وفعل مضارع صيغة ٢", eg: "Purposive lām and Verb Imperfect 2nd form", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "(II)", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "SUBJ", lu: "عَذَابٌ،يُعَذِّبُ"},
"33:73:2" : {s: 33, a: 73, w: 2, r: "اله", t: "ٱللَّهُ", l: "ٱللَّه", lc: 2811, tl: "l-lahu", lb: "আল্লাহ",e: "So that Allah may punish", b: "আল্লাহ", i: "Allah", f: 733, rm: "to serve, worship or adore; to protect, grant refuge, preserve save, rescue, liberate; object of worship ie God; (ا-ل-ل-ه) God, the one true God applied as a proper name denoting the true god, comprising all the excellent divine names; a unity comprising all the essences of existing things.", ag: "علم مرفوع", eg: "Proper Nominative case", tag: "PN", pos: "PN", att: "NOM", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "", num: "", mood: "", lu: "إِلَٰهٌۭ"},
"33:73:3" : {s: 33, a: 73, w: 3, r: "نفق", t: "ٱلْمُنَٰفِقِينَ", l: "مُنَٰفِقُون", lc: 27, tl: "l-munāfiqīna", lb: "খরচকারী, ব্যয়কারী",e: "the hypocrite men", b: "মুনাফিক পুরুষদেরকে", i: "orang-orang munafik laki-laki", f: 15, rm: "to be saleable, to come out of a hole, be exhausted (store), consumed, spent, expenditure. To enter into another hole where there is another outlet, so is a hypocrite who professes to believe first one thing and then another, thus entering faith through one door and leaving it through another.", ag: "ال التعريف وأسم فاعل", eg: "Determiner al and Noun Active participle", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACT_PCPL", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَنفَقَ،مُنَٰفِقُونَ"},
"33:73:4" : {s: 33, a: 73, w: 4, r: "نفق", t: "وَٱلْمُنَٰفِقَٰتِ", l: "مُنَٰفِقَٰت", lc: 5, tl: "wal-munāfiqāti", lb: "মুনাফিক নারী",e: "and the hypocrite women", b: "ও মুনাফিক নারীদেরকে", i: "dan orang munafik perempuan", f: 3, rm: "to be saleable, to come out of a hole, be exhausted (store), consumed, spent, expenditure. To enter into another hole where there is another outlet, so is a hypocrite who professes to believe first one thing and then another, thus entering faith through one door and leaving it through another.", ag: "واو عطف وال التعريف وأسم فاعل", eg: "Conjunction wa and Determiner al and Noun Active participle", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACT_PCPL", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "F", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَنفَقَ،مُنَٰفِقُونَ"},
"33:73:5" : {s: 33, a: 73, w: 5, r: "شرك", t: "وَٱلْمُشْرِكِينَ", l: "مُشْرِك", lc: 44, tl: "wal-mush'rikīna", lb: "মুশরিক, যে আল্লাহর সাথে অংশীদার সাব্যস্ত করে, শিরককারী, অংশীদার স্থাপনকারী",e: "and the polytheist men", b: "এবং মুশরিক পুরুষদেরকে", i: "dan orang musyrik laki-laki", f: 4, rm: "to be a companion, be sharer/partner. shirkun - share, participation, polytheism, idolatry, making associate/partner with Allah. shariik (pl. shurakaa) - associate, partner, sharer. Nouns of the second declension when followed by the affixed pronouns take the three inflexions thus shurakaa, shurakaai, shurakaaa. shaarak (vb. 3) - to share with. ashraka (vb. 4) - to make a sharer or associate, give companions (e.g. to God), be a polytheist or idolater. ashraktumuuni - you associated me as partner. mushrik - one who gives associate to God, polytheist. mushtarikun (vb. 8) - one who partakes or shares.", ag: "واو عطف وال التعريف وأسم فاعل", eg: "Conjunction wa and Determiner al and Noun Active participle", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACT_PCPL", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَشْرَكَ،شُرَكَآءُ،شُرَكَٰٓؤُا۟،يُشْرِكُ"},
